org.openflow.protocol.factory

Class BasicFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.factory.BasicFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OFActionFactory, OFExperimenterDataFactory, OFInstructionFactory, OFMessageFactory, OFStatisticsFactory, SMMessageFactory

    public class BasicFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements OFMessageFactory, OFActionFactory, OFInstructionFactory, OFStatisticsFactory, OFExperimenterDataFactory, SMMessageFactory
    A basic OpenFlow factory that supports naive creation of both Messages and Actions.
    Author:
    David Erickson (daviderickson@cs.stanford.edu), Rob Sherwood (rob.sherwood@stanford.edu)

      • getExperimenterData

        public OFExperimenterData getExperimenterData(OFExperimenterId vendorId,
                                     OFExperimenterDataType vendorDataType)
        Description copied from interface: OFExperimenterDataFactory
        Retrieves an OFVendorData instance corresponding to the specified OFVendorId and OFVendorDataType. There are 3 possible cases for how this will be called: 1) If the vendor id in the OFVendor message is an unknown value, then this method is called with both vendorId and vendorDataType set to null. In this case typically the factory method should return an instance of OFGenericVendorData that just contains the raw byte array of the vendor data. 2) If the vendor id is known but no vendor data type has been registered for the data in the message, then vendorId is set to the appropriate OFVendorId instance and OFVendorDataType is set to null. This would typically be handled the same way as #1 3) If both the vendor id and and vendor data type are known, then typically you'd just call the method in OFVendorDataType to instantiate the appropriate subclass of OFVendorData.
        Specified by:
        getExperimenterData in interface OFExperimenterDataFactory
        Parameters:
        vendorId - the experimenterId of the containing OFVendor message
        vendorDataType - the type of the OFExperimenterData to be retrieved
        Returns:
        an OFExperimenterData instance
